{"tid":1920943,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"壯陽 補身 健康 營養豐富超級食品討論","createTime":"2020-03-11T19:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T15:40:22.000Z","uid":13745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ca2140291c0e70456a9a7542d1fba63a90812b39","tid":1920943,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T19:35:39.000Z","msg":"最近知道有樣超級食物叫椰棗<br />\n產自中東 功效超多<br />\n<a href=\"https://food.ulifestyle.com.hk/restaurant/news/detail/2401014/椰棗營養-營養師推介月經必吃高鐵中東椰棗-7大營養價值-內附食譜\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffood.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Frestaurant%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F2401014%2F%E6%A4%B0%E6%A3%97%E7%87%9F%E9%A4%8A-%E7%87%9F%E9%A4%8A%E5%B8%AB%E6%8E%A8%E4%BB%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%85%E5%90%83%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1%E6%A4%B0%E6%A3%97-7%E5%A4%A7%E7%87%9F%E9%A4%8A%E5%83%B9%E5%80%BC-%E5%85%A7%E9%99%84%E9%A3%9F%E8%AD%9C&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stkpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=a748c7c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://food.ulifestyle.com.hk/restaurant/news/detail/2401014/椰棗營養-營養師推介月經必吃高鐵中東椰棗-7大營養價值-內附食譜</a><br />\n例如 有磷、鉀、鈣、鎂等礦物質，有助保持骨骼健康，預防骨質疏鬆。<br />\n補充體能<br />\n椰棗有較豐富的抗氧化物成分。當中包括類黃酮（Flavonoids）、類胡蘿蔔素（Carotenoids）和酚酸（Phenolic acid），有助預防心臟病、癌症、腦退化症和糖尿病<br />\n高鐵同高鉀  有助降血壓 預防貧血<br />\n聽聞重可以壯陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知呢度有冇巴打試過係咪堅壯陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就買過 citysuper Kluth 德國冇核椰棗 成$50一包<br />\n味道口感唔錯 有咬口 甜度適中<br />\n亦都上網買過有核中東椰棗 味道口感大約同上"},{"pid":"a1e1e4c2c4f1d558470edc690c5a00a41101b285","tid":1920943,"uid":307685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T19:42:30.000Z","msg":"蝙蝠"},{"pid":"6ed41c3467fd727481706af2c96e255fc301bc66","tid":1920943,"